================================================================================

This derivative work includes the following modifications and enhancements:

1. Comprehensive error handling system with custom error types (errors.go)
2. Extensive test coverage:
   - Core redaction tests (redactor_test.go)
   - Import handling tests (imports_test.go)
   - Validation tests (validation_test.go)
   - Optional fields tests (optional_fields_test.go)
   - Integration tests (integration_test.go)
   - External template tests (external_template_test.go)
   - Error handling tests (errors_test.go)

3. Bug fixes:
   - Fixed proto3 optional field pointer assignment (fields.go, module.go)
   - Corrected type casting for optional numeric fields
   - Fixed bytes field handling (always []byte, never *[]byte)

4. New features:
   - Custom template file support (module.go, external_template_test.go)
   - Enhanced validation with detailed error messages
   - Integration tests with actual protoc compilation
   - Debug logging and panic recovery

5. Documentation improvements:
   - Custom template guide (examples/CUSTOM_TEMPLATE.md)
   - Example template file (examples/custom-template.tmpl)
   - Updated README with advanced features section

All modifications are contributed under the Apache License 2.0.

